description: Creates and returns a URL that you can use to access the application UIs for a job run. For jobs in a running state, the application UI is a live user interface such as the Spark or Tez web UI. For completed jobs, the application UI is a persistent application user interface such as the Spark History Server or persistent Tez UI.

parameters.name: jobRunId
parameters.description: The ID of the job run.

nested_items.name: url
nested_items.description: The URL to view job run's dashboard.
